So this class looks more familiar to our readers, let's please follow the Java bean convention, like so:
public class EmailData implements Serializable {
    private String subject;
    private String content;

    // ...

    public String getSubject() {
        return this.subject;
    }

    // ...
}
instead of using a repository list and constants.

